!requirements.txt

# ==============================================================================
# Notes:
# ==============================================================================
# - TensorRT engines are GPU-specific and must be built at runtime
# - Model files (.pt) can be downloaded at runtime to reduce image size
# - Logs and output should be mounted as volumes
# - The .dockerignore reduces build context and image size significantly
# ==============================================================================
